        <updateDate>2023-03-10T18:27:15Z</updateDate>
        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Codification of Verified Values Act or the CVV Act&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;This bill requires a contributor to political organizations who uses a credit card to make online contributions to such organizations to disclose the credit verification value of such credit card at the time a contribution is made. A credit verification value is a series of numbers on a credit card (usually on the back of the card) that provides additional security for a transaction by credit card.&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
